{"tid":1833531,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海關單野睇得出有幾多分化撚","createTime":"2020-01-22T02:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-22T03:55:20.000Z","uid":182990,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fe19cf49a1aa834117417ab983ecfc9c4f37fdfc","tid":1833531,"uid":182990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:55:04.000Z","msg":"首先 臨過年先發生呢件事 真係唔開心<br />\n<br />\n其次 船隊一定唔係特務警，唔會有人PT幫手 轉得過去 佢係唔會再出現係海關<br />\n<br />\n而家有部分人 一聽到係紀律部隊4隻字就係又屌唔係又屌<br />\n邊個係金鐘站開閘比手足? <br />\n仲有被停職既消防，海關，救護<br />\n甚至話做公務員已經被人話係狗 <br />\n<br />\n我屌9哂你地 8月2號 公務員集會 有幾多人出席？<br />\n<br />\n當中有幾多人係AO EO 政府既行政人員，<br />\n亦有機會係未來有決策權既人 <br />\n<br />\n而你地？剩係識對住部電腦屌 乜撚野人都割<br />\n再咁落去 不如你地直接叫連登獨立啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然 希望搞分化既係5毛 唔係手足<br />\n<br />\n最後 願死者安息"},{"pid":"52594ec71b52acf156fd700adbacde06aa74ca81","tid":1833531,"uid":161404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:56:50.000Z","msg":"Rip"},{"pid":"bbae0d69a371356d871f3e28c0d0c97ed50535ee","tid":1833531,"uid":69707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T02:57:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/bmbqnd1y2tQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fbmbqnd1y2tQ&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=c5962a9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/bmbqnd1y2tQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZKjtBc74Vs0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZKjtBc74Vs0&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=9d34d39c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZKjtBc74Vs0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SZNWaAaM7XY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSZNWaAaM7XY&d=fvWYig%2FFXUG8IHhaG2JvmLXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=e74cb273\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SZNWaAaM7XY</a><br />\n自己用下個腦諗下"},{"pid":"9c7a34222f681d57b0cc2054e6e8f672365fb81f","tid":1833531,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0